Projects

E-Commerce Website Development

  • Developed a fully functional e-commerce website using React.js for the frontend and Node.js for the backend.
  • Implemented features like product listing, user authentication, and shopping cart functionality.
  • Optimized performance and responsiveness for various devices and browsers, improving load time by 30%.

Social Media Dashboard

  • Created a social media analytics dashboard using React.js and Redux for state management.
  • Integrated RESTful APIs to fetch and display real-time data, increasing data retrieval efficiency by 25%.
  • Enhanced user experience by implementing dynamic charts and data visualization, resulting in a 20% increase in user engagement.

Task Management Application

  • Designed and developed a task management application using Node.js and Express framework.
  • Implemented user authentication and CRUD operations for tasks.
  • Used MongoDB for data storage solutions and optimized database queries for performance, reducing query time by 40%.
